Research Question 2: What are most common names given to dogs¶

From the above image, we can deduce that "Cooper" is the most common name given to dogs, This can be better visualized with a Wordcloud

Research Question 3: What is the most often and lowest rating given to dogs¶

Insight: Ratings 12/10 is most often given to dogs while 2/10 is the least given to dogs

We also proceeded to examine why a dog got 2/10 rating

Crystal, a Maltese dog breed got a 2/10 rating and we proceeded to have a visual assessment as to why

Above is a picture of Crystal, with the tweet text

"This is Crystal. She's a shitty fireman. No sense of urgency. People could be dying Crystal. 2/10 just irresponsible "

A bit harsh, Lol. Because Crystal look like a "firedog" i would 80% trust with my life, would give her 13/10 if i could
